 <text id="F3063T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus says he hopes to come home soon and have a doctor put a piece a silver in his wounded
     head.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1863-01-09"><orig reg="January">Jenary</orig> the 9th 1863</date>
      <name type="place">Morris <orig reg="island">iland</orig> south <orig reg="Carolina">Carlina</orig></name>
     </dateline>
     <salute><orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear</salute>
    </opener>

    <p>it is With the <orig reg="greatest">grates</orig> of <orig reg="pleasure">pleaser</orig> that
     I <orig reg="take">tak</orig> this <orig reg="opportunity">optuity</orig> to <orig reg="inform"
      >in form</orig> you that I am Well at Present and i hope <orig reg="When">Whean</orig>
     <orig reg="these">thes</orig>
     <orig reg="few">fu</orig> lines <orig reg="Come">Com</orig> to hand <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="may">ma</orig> find you in the <orig reg="greatest">grates</orig> of <orig
      reg="pleasure">pleas</orig> i <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig> a <orig reg="wrote">rote</orig>
     <orig reg="sooner">sonner</orig> but i Was <orig reg="Disappointed">Disaponte</orig> i <orig
      reg="start">starte</orig> home <orig reg="for">fer</orig> me and Jacop A Watson Was to <orig
      reg="get">git</orig>
     <orig reg="our">ar</orig>
     <orig reg="furlough">forlow</orig>
     <orig reg="about">a boute</orig>
     <orig reg="two">too</orig>
     <orig reg="Weeks">Weaks</orig>
     <orig reg="ago">a go</orig> and We never got them yet but i am <orig reg="looking"
     >loking</orig> for them day after <orig reg="tomorrow">to morrow</orig> and you <orig
      reg="need">nead</orig> not to <orig reg="write">rite</orig> till you get <orig reg="another">a
      nether</orig> letter <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i <orig reg="may">ma</orig> be <orig
      reg="home">hom</orig> in <orig reg="two">too</orig>
     <orig reg="Weeks">Weaks</orig> but i <orig reg="Can't">Cant</orig> tell you how <orig
      reg="soon">son</orig> but i <orig reg="haven't">havte</orig> got a letter from you <orig
      reg="for">fer</orig> five Weeks <orig reg="about">abut</orig> i <orig reg="thought">thot</orig>
     <orig reg="maybe">mabey</orig> you Was so <orig reg="busy">bisey</orig> that you had not time
     to <orig reg="write">rite</orig> but i hope that i Will find you Well <orig reg="When"
     >Whean</orig> i <orig reg="Do">Dow</orig>
     <orig reg="Come">Com</orig> i got a letter <orig reg="from">frum</orig> John and he say that he
      <orig reg="don't">dont</orig>
     <orig reg="know">now</orig>
     <orig reg="What">Waot</orig> to <orig reg="do">dou</orig> but tell him to stay at <orig
      reg="home">hom</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i am Coming <orig reg="home">hom</orig> to stay i am not able to
      <unclear>stan</unclear> the <orig reg="army">armey</orig> since i Was <orig reg="Wounded"
      >Wonded</orig> the <unclear>least</unclear> thing for <orig reg="my">mi</orig>
     <orig reg="head">hed</orig> but i think if i get <orig reg="home">hom</orig> and go to <orig
      reg="doctor">docter</orig> harmen <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> i <orig reg="Can">Con</orig> get
     a <orig reg="piece">peas</orig> of silver <orig reg="put">poot</orig> on the hole <orig
      reg="Why">Wiy</orig> i think that it Will get Well i must bring <orig reg="my">mi</orig>
     letter to a Close by sending you a <orig reg="sweet">sweat</orig> kiss good <orig reg="night"
      >nighte</orig> give <orig reg="my">mi</orig> love to all <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
     <orig reg="friend">frend</orig>
    </p>

    <closer>
     <salute><orig reg="your">yor</orig> Dear <orig reg="husband">husben</orig></salute>
     <signed>David <orig reg="Andrew">Andred</orig> Demus</signed>
     <seg type="postscript"> to Mrs Mrs <orig reg="Mary">Marrey</orig> Jane <orig reg="Demus"
      >Demes</orig><lb/> the lily of the flore </seg>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
